Comment: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:35.46,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}憧れを書きとめて
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.21,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}いつか叶える日のために
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:43.68,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折り目つけたあのページを　開きたい時がきた
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:49.02,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}巻き起こるアレコレで　見失うこともあるけれど
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.77,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}ねっ、大丈夫　踏み出してる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.40,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}はじまりは想定外
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:57.19,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}君が消せないまま残した
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.94,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}寂しがりだった記憶さえ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:04.03,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}読み替えてみせるよ　明るい方へ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:09.45,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}たったそれだけで全てが変わる気がするから
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.75,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:13.79,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}だから　さあおいで　そのままで！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:16.63,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}弱虫も隠さないで
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:17.84,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.51,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}夢乗せ　待ち合わせよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:27.39,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}この冒険記を綴る中　君の名を呼んでも
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:33.89,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}もう迷子じゃない　一緒の旅を始めよう
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:41.23,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}そう…きみと、わたし、もっと！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----OPlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:35.46,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}記下你的憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.59,0:01:38.21,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}以迎接它變成現實的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.30,0:01:43.68,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}折疊起來的書頁  正在呼喚著我去翻閱
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.72,0:01:49.02,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}揚起的風沙塵土  可能會讓你迷失方向
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.10,0:01:51.77,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但是不要擔心  我們在堅定前行
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.81,0:01:54.40,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}只是開端有點意想不到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.56,0:01:57.19,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}你記錄下的寂寞經歷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.27,0:01:59.94,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}無法擦去
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.99,0:02:04.03,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}但我會解讀成未來的財富
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.07,0:02:09.45,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}如此小的努力就能讓我感到世界煥然一新
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.58,0:02:10.75,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}All Right
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.83,0:02:13.79,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}所以  跟我來吧  就這樣出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.83,0:02:16.63,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒有什麼好害怕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.75,0:02:17.84,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}"On my Sheep"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.92,0:02:21.51,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}放飛夢想  相約明天
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.67,0:02:27.39,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}書寫這篇歷險記的時候  即使呼喚你的名字
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.47,0:02:33.89,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}那也不意味著迷路  而是共同啟程的信號
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.98,0:02:41.23,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}沒錯…你與我 不會停步！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcJPN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:53.81,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}始まりのベル　鍵をかける音
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:22:01.61,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}流れゆく間に大人になる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:07.35,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}走り　はしゃぎ　過ごす日々が
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:11.59,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}遠ざかるときがくる
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:16.09,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ここで出した答えを
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:28.28,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}ああ　どこかで語り継げたら
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:33.56,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}迷いながら歩く人波を
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:37.89,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}照らし出す光になれるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:46.10,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}包まれてたグリーンベルトの先
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:54.44,OPlrcJPN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}続く明日を目指してる
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----EDlrcCHN-----
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.50,0:21:53.81,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}起始之鈴  上鎖之聲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.36,0:22:01.61,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}在它們的流淌中  我們逐漸成長
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.88,0:22:07.35,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}奔跑歡笑的日子
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.71,0:22:11.59,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}終歸會遠去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.91,0:22:16.09,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}此刻得出的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.09,0:22:28.28,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}只要將它流傳下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.09,0:22:33.56,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}即使是迷惘而行的人潮
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.82,0:22:37.89,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}也能將其引領
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.00,0:22:46.10,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}沿著綠蔭大道走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.31,0:22:54.44,OPlrcCHN,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}就能到達期望的明天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-----TXT-----
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.64,0:00:02.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,夏天了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.57,0:00:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今年第一次來泳池
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:07.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打起精神來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.43,0:00:10.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起把泳池打掃得閃閃發亮吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.39,0:00:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.16,0:00:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.04,0:00:23.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然來泳池了  真想欣賞穿泳裝的姐姐們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.69,0:00:26.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高峰  別廢話快幹活
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.89,TXTB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs\frz21.52\pos(78.667,177.334)}圖書部\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h嘗百麵調查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.89,TXTB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\frz21.52\pos(110,223.334)}活動內容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.89,TXTB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\frz21.52\pos(125.333,260)}調查學校周邊的拉麵店菜單！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.89,TXTB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\frz21.52\pos(111.334,304.667)}選出圖書部的推薦菜單！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.89,TXTB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\fs12\frz21.52\pos(158.666,317.334)}委託內容
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.09,0:00:31.89,TXTB,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs12\frz21.52\pos(207.999,352)}請把學園附近拉麵店的\N推薦品項告訴我們！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.96,0:00:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我喜歡拉麵  不過吃不下了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.71,0:00:42.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叉燒我要了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.50,0:00:46.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助你還能吃得下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.32,0:00:48.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肉是裝在我另一個胃的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.32,0:00:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,話說  我們真是受歡迎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.06,0:00:55.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都累得一塌糊塗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.43,0:00:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是發傳單的成果呀
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.45,0:01:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想消除記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:06.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那讓圖書部的知名度提高了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.16,0:01:09.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但都是些雜活啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.41,0:01:11.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不要在意這些了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.85,0:01:15.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去完成下一件委託吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.31,0:01:18.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好當是飯後運動
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.84,0:01:21.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒完啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.58,0:03:13.34,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz16.95\pos(508.666,183.333)\blur1.7\fad(250,880)}我要怎樣才能跟你見面？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.16,0:03:13.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到會有回信
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.00,0:03:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧羊人在我身邊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.03,0:03:32.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是石牆研究會的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.70,0:03:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎麼做才能讓大家領會到石牆的魅力？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.15,0:03:35.65,TXTD,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}原野砌法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.15,0:03:35.65,TXTD,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9}龜甲砌法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.22,0:03:40.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請告訴我和女友破鏡重圓的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.04,0:03:46.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天我要參加打工的面試  很緊張
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.10,0:03:49.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請教給我不緊張的魔法
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.80,0:03:54.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這學園淨是有煩惱的傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.10,0:03:58.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都是迷途的羔羊呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.52,0:04:03.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們能不能收斂些
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.52,0:04:05.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很多來投訴你們的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.32,0:04:09.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是誰
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.62,0:04:10.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誰來著…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.03,0:04:12.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想想…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.01,0:04:16.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們裝什麼傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.91,0:04:18.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她是圖書委員小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.35,0:04:21.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  對
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.44,0:04:23.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼說起來
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.70,0:04:24.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好過份
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.87,0:04:27.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們不是一起洗過澡嗎  洗衣板
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.65,0:04:29.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒到洗衣板的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.30,0:04:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫成品格的品
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.46,0:04:33.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是品乳
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.28,0:04:35.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是小太刀同學
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.84,0:04:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  你住在筧的隔壁
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.10,0:04:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別說這個了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.94,0:04:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書委員長找你們有事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.15,0:04:45.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說希望你們盡快離開這個活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.74,0:04:52.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最近活動室的利用情況很不妥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.54,0:04:54.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你們圖書部成員能換個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.89,0:04:58.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以配合現在的活動
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.96,0:05:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  我們會想對策的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.59,0:05:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以請讓我們繼續留在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.20,0:05:12.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要我們做什麼都行
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能給我們個機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.37,0:05:19.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就設個緩刑期吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.43,0:05:24.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  這可真累
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.88,0:05:28.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但弄乾淨後一定會有好評
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:31.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也能提升圖書委員對我們的印象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.68,0:05:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油保護我們的活動室吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.99,0:05:38.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}好  圖書部保衛戰開始啦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天都很忙呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.51,0:05:42.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,望月學姐
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.40,0:05:45.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽圖書委員長說了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.51,0:05:49.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戶外的筧感覺真是新鮮
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.38,0:05:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太陽這麼耀眼  我都快成人乾了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.03,0:05:56.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但為了保住活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.21,0:05:58.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不能再介意日曬了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.59,0:06:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你變了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.94,0:06:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是圖書部成員的影響嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.82,0:06:06.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.46,0:06:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己感覺不出來
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.89,0:06:13.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧同學  要不要進學生會
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.00,0:06:16.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來發現自己更多新的一面
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.90,0:06:21.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,差一點就能見到其他的東西了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.90,0:06:24.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.33,0:06:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開玩笑的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:28.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  你太壞心眼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.54,0:06:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.35,0:06:34.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今後的面談要通過郵件預約
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.28,0:06:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面談時間每人最多三十分鐘
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.59,0:06:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,依照預約時間讓學生來活動室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.72,0:06:44.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,累了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.98,0:06:46.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.57,0:06:47.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.52,0:06:52.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小玉  你不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.73,0:06:55.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很快就完  你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.46,0:06:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我幫你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.70,0:06:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用  小事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.44,0:07:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天見
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻庭她不要緊吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.44,0:07:10.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們的事務工作都是她一個人幹
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.35,0:07:12.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再加上這次的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.11,0:07:15.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得她應該很累
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.06,0:07:17.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是會示弱的人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.54,0:07:24.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊  但把負擔都交給一個人不好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.71,0:07:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你很關心我們社團嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.09,0:07:29.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.43,0:07:35.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你會把圖書部說成「我們」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.50,0:07:42.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.19,0:07:46.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,適合做牧羊人的是我
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.84,0:08:08.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但把負擔都交給一個人不好
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.92,0:08:11.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,應該不會吧…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.14,0:08:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你果然在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.88,0:08:24.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻庭
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.32,TXTE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,135.333)}魚兒占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.32,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,220)}{\1c&H3314D6&}Q{\r}「無法拒絕別人的委託」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.90,0:08:29.32,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,302)}{\1c&H3314D6&}A{\r}  是/否/都說不上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:35.41,TXTE,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,135.333)}魚兒占卜
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:35.41,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,220)}{\1c&H3314D6&}Q{\r}「經常被人說是優柔寡斷」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.40,0:08:35.41,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(320,302)}{\1c&H3314D6&}A{\r}  是/否/都說不上
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.40,0:08:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,選哪個啊  也算不上優柔寡斷…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:40.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  嗯…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.75,0:08:42.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.33,0:08:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「都說不上」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.24,0:08:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全是優柔寡斷吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.61,0:08:49.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  都答完了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.72,0:08:51.38,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(513.333,274.667)}你是{\1c&H89EA91&}「藤壺」{\r}型
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.67,0:08:52.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤壺！？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.54,0:08:56.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藤壺也太扯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.27,0:08:57.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重來
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:58.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這怎麼樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.89,0:09:00.48,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(513.333,274.667)}你是{\1c&HE98CA8&}「海膽」{\r}型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.98,0:09:03.65,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(513.333,274.667)}你是{\1c&H79E2F0&}「海星」{\r}型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.23,0:09:05.86,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(530.666,274)}你是{\1c&HD489F5&}「海葵」{\r}型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.49,0:09:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託了  至少是魚
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.49,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(108.666,280.667)}你是{\1c&HC2DD8D&}「鯙」{\r}型
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:13.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好  魚類來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.32,0:09:17.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道厲害了吧  真是…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.81,0:09:20.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧？！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.11,0:09:29.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好險
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.06,0:09:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.63,0:09:38.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不是在玩
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.64,0:09:40.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,查東西時不自覺地就…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.39,0:09:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是安心了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.28,0:09:46.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本還以為你根本不會放鬆
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.49,0:09:56.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我應該更努力的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.03,0:09:58.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你已經做了很多了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.11,0:10:00.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有好好睡覺嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  沒問…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.16,0:10:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,題
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.52,0:10:08.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來是有問題呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.61,0:10:11.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠近些  不然會濕的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.35,0:10:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不努力的話  會感覺不安
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.88,0:10:32.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻庭你很努力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.41,0:10:36.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,圖書部可以說是靠你撐起來的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.69,0:10:40.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再放鬆些吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:42.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不快樂的話
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Happy  Project也沒意義
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.46,0:10:45.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.28,0:10:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.71,0:10:53.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.68,0:10:58.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雨停了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.35,0:11:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,櫻…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.17,0:11:18.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我離開的這段時間似乎發生了不少事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.19,0:11:22.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧京太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.87,0:11:25.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初試合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要再玩郵件遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.18,0:11:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道了？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.73,0:11:35.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的工作僅限於觀察他才對
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.37,0:11:40.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我失去資格了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:41.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.11,0:11:43.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但正如我以前說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.07,0:11:47.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這樣下去只能一直是牧羊人候選
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.15,0:11:55.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你缺少什麼  要你自己發覺才有意義
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.41,0:11:57.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:04.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是想成為牧羊人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可受不了被那傢伙搶先
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.88,0:12:23.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼啊  吵死人了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.85,0:12:27.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好  我是你可愛的鄰居  小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.21,0:12:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在夢裡見到真兇了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.08,0:12:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是預知夢嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.29,0:12:37.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧  你相信預知夢或者預見未來什麼的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.45,0:12:39.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼突然問這個
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.17,0:12:42.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能預見未來的話  還挺讓人頭疼的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.81,0:12:45.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果看到的都是光明的未來那還好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.85,0:12:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到黑暗的未來的話  會痛苦的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.41,0:12:55.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都是那傢伙說會受傷  才變成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.44,0:12:58.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好噁心啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.91,0:13:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說  筧你能看到未來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.09,0:13:06.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果我說能看到  你會相信嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.26,0:13:11.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我父母那方面的感覺很靈  所以我會相信吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.29,0:13:13.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.03,0:13:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,實際上  我偶爾會有像是第六感的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.72,0:13:23.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從以前我就常看到奇怪的圖書館的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.00,0:13:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延伸到遠方  沒有盡頭
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.33,0:13:31.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那裡有魔法之書
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.26,0:13:36.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上面寫滿了看不懂的文字
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:39.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當要看到其他人的未來的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.85,0:13:43.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎都會先看到圖書館的幻影
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.02,0:13:47.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  也看看我的未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.75,0:13:48.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.98,0:13:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就稍微看一看嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.66,0:13:56.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我話說在前頭  並不是每一次都能成功啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.22,0:14:02.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.88,0:14:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才那是…怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.20,0:14:29.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看到了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.75,0:14:34.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有一道看不見的牆  沒法再繼續前進
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.22,0:14:36.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看不見的牆？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.55,0:14:40.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那算什麼  真無聊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.56,0:14:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,端著酒杯泡在裝滿鈔票的浴缸裡的未來呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.53,0:14:45.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說啥呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.41,0:14:49.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺累了  回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.61,0:14:54.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管結果如何  反正你也幫我看了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:57.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就慶幸你沒看到壞的未來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.45,0:15:07.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,感覺就像是什麼都不存在  一片空白
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.54,0:15:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事至今為止還沒出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.42,0:15:18.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙…看得很清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.84,0:15:23.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧京太郎  初試合格了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.62,0:15:33.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牧羊人是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.62,0:15:36.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之我什麼都不知道  告辭了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.54,0:15:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.29,0:15:39.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.77,0:15:41.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是第三個了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.35,0:15:46.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說目擊到牧羊人的明明是她們…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會想不起來了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.00,0:15:51.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且三個人都是這麼說的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.22,0:15:55.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,記憶真能變得一片空白嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:57.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一片空白…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:02.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.61,0:16:06.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  買了好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.19,0:16:09.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有很多需要的用品嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.54,0:16:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有儀左大人的玩具
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.76,0:16:15.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經完全成為儀左大人的俘虜了呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.26,0:16:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助  你吃醋了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.46,0:16:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為組合的一員  有一點吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.68,0:16:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,組合？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯  如花似玉的一年級組合
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.63,0:16:25.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助&御園同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.25,0:16:27.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,直接用真名啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.59,0:16:31.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈助…真好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.78,0:16:32.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,御園同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.17,0:16:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  叫我時不用加上同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.68,0:16:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就  御園
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.47,0:16:40.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就叫你千莉
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.10,0:16:42.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然就直呼其名了？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.49,0:16:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我們是組合嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.64,0:16:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得有成立過啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.44,0:16:47.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就面臨解散危機了！？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.40,0:16:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.98,0:16:50.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我也沒辦法呀
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.18,0:16:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,佳奈你真是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.13,0:16:56.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛  剛才你叫我佳奈了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:17:00.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是對你直呼其名的回應而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.98,0:17:02.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣也沒問題  千莉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.08,0:17:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再叫一次
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.84,0:17:11.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是…小太刀學姐？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.83,0:17:13.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  你們先回去
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.34,0:17:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.66,0:17:20.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.08,0:17:29.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.35,0:17:30.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,關於昨晚的事
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.80,0:17:36.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.01,0:17:41.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚是指…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.11,0:17:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生了什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.73,0:17:53.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.36,0:17:58.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:02.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那兩人太可疑了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.59,0:18:06.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧學長說了「昨晚的事」什麼的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:08.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是兩人一起過夜了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.38,0:18:10.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太不檢點了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.59,0:18:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人和女人夜裡獨處一室
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.06,0:18:15.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}不行
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.59,0:18:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肯定不會發生什麼正經的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.65,0:18:21.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.61,0:18:25.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那  那兩個人關係有那麼好嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.72,0:18:27.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎學姐  茶都灑出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.89,0:18:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動搖得好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.97,0:18:31.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是呢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.12,0:18:34.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕…絕無此事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.98,0:18:36.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對不對不對
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.68,0:18:38.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有我們的容身之地呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:03.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她…究竟…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:14.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.02,0:19:16.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在說話方便嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.89,0:19:19.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想問一下你下週的計劃
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.09,0:19:20.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你星期二有空嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.98,0:19:24.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別  別誤會  才不是邀請你去約會
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.64,0:19:25.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.50,0:19:27.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我到底在說些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.60,0:19:29.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  還沒回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.76,0:19:31.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀  抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.16,0:19:32.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我馬上就回去
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.92,0:19:33.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.46,0:19:36.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筧？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:39.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我星期二有時間
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.00,0:19:42.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不論是搬東西還是要打掃  都沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.26,0:19:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  幫大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.49,0:19:47.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在下雨呢  帶傘了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.05,0:19:50.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天…帶了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.86,0:19:52.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  那早點回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.34,0:19:55.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.87,0:20:06.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吵死了  你以為現在幾點啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.94,0:20:10.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs18}有事去門口說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.40,0:20:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀  為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.61,0:20:15.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  有完沒完呀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.07,0:20:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說住在這裡…是騙人的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.46,0:20:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白崎她們之前好像也忘記了你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.01,0:20:40.76,TXTC,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs25\frz16.95\pos(508.666,183.333)\blur1.7\fad(250,880)}我要怎樣才能跟你見面？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.79,0:20:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.51,0:20:46.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你就是牧羊人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.18,0:20:50.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然變成這樣了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.81,0:20:51.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.76,0:20:55.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就是給你們發郵件的牧羊人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.04,0:21:00.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恭喜你
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.50,0:21:08.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你初試合格了  筧京太郎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是我對你合格表示的祝賀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.23,0:21:22.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼  走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.77,0:21:26.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去魔法圖書館
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.30,0:21:30.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,魔法…圖書館？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.63,0:23:09.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  為什麼我必須祝賀筧啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.80,0:23:11.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老大也真欺負人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.48,0:23:13.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧  既然那麼想讓我慶祝的話
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.36,0:23:15.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就來個特大號的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.37,0:23:17.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀妹妹特製
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.29,0:23:19.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,混蛋筧給我炸飛吧豪華版！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.25,0:23:22.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,惹怒我的代價是很沉重的喔
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.78,0:23:24.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小太刀妹妹  加油
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.21,0:23:28.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SHOOTING  STAR！
